  "title": "The genius behind some of the world's most famous buildings | Renzo Piano",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12817.0,
      "end_time": 15738.0,
      "text": "Architecture is amazing, for sure."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 17357.0,
      "end_time": 19761.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s amazing because it&#39;s art."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 20659.0,
      "end_time": 23370.0,
      "text": "But you know, it&#39;s a very funny kind of art."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 23610.0,
      "end_time": 26937.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s an art at the frontier between art and science."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 27593.0,
      "end_time": 29509.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s fed by ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 31530.0,
      "end_time": 33150.0,
      "text": "by real life, every day."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 33631.0,
      "end_time": 36376.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s driven by force of necessity."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 37313.0,
      "end_time": 39837.0,
      "text": "Quite amazing, quite amazing."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 39861.0,
      "end_time": 43480.0,
      "text": "And the life of the architect is also amazing."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 45480.0,
      "end_time": 48175.0,
      "text": "You know, as an architect, at 10 oâ€™clock in the morning,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 48199.0,
      "end_time": 51309.0,
      "text": "you need to be a poet, for sure."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 51333.0,
      "end_time": 53741.0,
      "text": "But at 11,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 53765.0,
      "end_time": 56371.0,
      "text": "you must become a humanist,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 56395.0,
      "end_time": 58751.0,
      "text": "otherwise you&#39;d lose your direction."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 59792.0,
      "end_time": 64210.0,
      "text": "And at noon, you absolutely need to be a builder."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 64936.00000000001,
      "end_time": 68467.0,
      "text": "You need to be able to make a building,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 68491.0,
      "end_time": 73382.0,
      "text": "because architecture, at the end, is the art of making buildings."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 73910.0,
      "end_time": 78487.0,
      "text": "Architecture is the art of making shelter for human beings."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 79370.0,
      "end_time": 80520.0,
      "text": "Period."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 80878.0,
      "end_time": 82745.0,
      "text": "And this is not easy at all."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 83600.0,
      "end_time": 84210.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s amazing."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 85380.0,
      "end_time": 86188.0,
      "text": "Look at this."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 87427.0,
      "end_time": 89482.0,
      "text": "Here we are in London,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 89506.0,
      "end_time": 94115.0,
      "text": "at the top of the Shard of Glass."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 95309.0,
      "end_time": 98964.0,
      "text": "This is a building we completed a few years ago."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 98988.0,
      "end_time": 104709.0,
      "text": "Those people are well-trained workers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 105845.0,
      "end_time": 109963.0,
      "text": "and they are assembling the top piece of the tower."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 111186.0,
      "end_time": 116500.0,
      "text": "Well, they look like rock climbers."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 116740.0,
      "end_time": 117224.0,
      "text": "They are."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 117575.0,
      "end_time": 120210.0,
      "text": "I mean, they are defying the force of gravity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 120234.0,
      "end_time": 122434.0,
      "text": "like building does, by the way."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 123607.0,
      "end_time": 125924.0,
      "text": "We got 30 of those people --"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 125948.0,
      "end_time": 130816.0,
      "text": "actually, on that site, we got more than 1,400 people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 130840.0,
      "end_time": 134502.0,
      "text": "coming from 60 different nationalities."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 135780.0,
      "end_time": 138930.0,
      "text": "You know, this is a miracle. It&#39;s a miracle."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 138117.0,
      "end_time": 141370.0,
      "text": "To put together 1,400 people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 141394.0,
      "end_time": 144474.0,
      "text": "coming from such different places, is a miracle."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 144847.0,
      "end_time": 146596.0,
      "text": "Sites are miracles."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 147157.0,
      "end_time": 148423.0,
      "text": "This is another one."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 149339.0,
      "end_time": 150795.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s talk about construction."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 150819.0,
      "end_time": 154736.0,
      "text": "Adventure, it&#39;s adventure in real life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 154760.0,
      "end_time": 156712.0,
      "text": "not adventure in spirit."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 157211.0,
      "end_time": 161133.0,
      "text": "This guy there is a deepwater diver."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 161157.0,
      "end_time": 165244.0,
      "text": "From rock climbers to deepwater divers."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 165268.0,
      "end_time": 167290.0,
      "text": "This is in Berlin."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 167530.0,
      "end_time": 169966.0,
      "text": "After the fall of the Wall in &#39;89,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 169990.0,
      "end_time": 174930.0,
      "text": "we built this building, connecting East Berlin to West Berlin,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 174117.0,
      "end_time": 175720.0,
      "text": "in Potsdamer Platz."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 176157.0,
      "end_time": 181177.0,
      "text": "We got on that project almost 5,000 people."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 182650.0,
      "end_time": 183796.0,
      "text": "Almost 5,000 people."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 184606.0,
      "end_time": 187858.0,
      "text": "And this is another site in Japan,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 188701.0,
      "end_time": 191250.0,
      "text": "building the Kansai Airport."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 191500.0,
      "end_time": 194201.0,
      "text": "Again, all the rock climbers, Japanese ones."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 194962.0,
      "end_time": 197803.0,
      "text": "You know, making buildings together"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 197827.0,
      "end_time": 202300.0,
      "text": "is the best way to create a sense of cooperation."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 202411.0,
      "end_time": 205231.0,
      "text": "The sense of pride -- pride is essential."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 206117.0,
      "end_time": 209505.0,
      "text": "But, you know, construction, of course,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 210633.0,
      "end_time": 214376.0,
      "text": "is one of the reasons why architecture is amazing."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 214824.0,
      "end_time": 219230.0,
      "text": "But there is another one, that is maybe even more amazing."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 219697.0,
      "end_time": 222315.0,
      "text": "Because architecture is the art"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 222339.0,
      "end_time": 227887.0,
      "text": "of making shelter for communities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 227911.0,
      "end_time": 229693.0,
      "text": "not just for individuals --"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 230380.0,
      "end_time": 233420.0,
      "text": "communities and society at large."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 233792.0,
      "end_time": 235792.0,
      "text": "And society is never the same."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 236792.0,
      "end_time": 238609.0,
      "text": "The world keeps changing."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 239950.0,
      "end_time": 243149.0,
      "text": "And changes are difficult to swallow by people."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 243498.0,
      "end_time": 247649.0,
      "text": "And architecture is a mirror of those changes."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 248140.0,
      "end_time": 253612.0,
      "text": "Architecture is the built expression of those changes."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 254347.0,
      "end_time": 258674.0,
      "text": "So, this is why it is so difficult,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 259411.0,
      "end_time": 263836.0,
      "text": "because those changes create adventure."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 264514.0,
      "end_time": 267244.0,
      "text": "They create adventure, and architecture is adventure."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 267268.0,
      "end_time": 270933.0,
      "text": "This is the Centre Georges Pompidou in Paris,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 270958.0,
      "end_time": 272133.0,
      "text": "a long time ago."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 272459.0,
      "end_time": 275777.0,
      "text": "That was back in time, &#39;77."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 276623.0,
      "end_time": 281170.0,
      "text": "This was a spaceship landing in the middle of Paris."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 282456.0,
      "end_time": 287329.0,
      "text": "Together with my friend in adventure, Richard Rogers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 287353.0,
      "end_time": 291101.0,
      "text": "we were, at the time, young bad boys."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 291125.0,
      "end_time": 292329.0,
      "text": "Young, bad boys."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 292353.0,
      "end_time": 293388.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 293412.0,
      "end_time": 298178.0,
      "text": "It was really only a few years after May &#39;68."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 298863.0,
      "end_time": 302770.0,
      "text": "So it was a rebellion, pure rebellion."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 302101.0,
      "end_time": 305133.0,
      "text": "The idea was to make"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 305688.0,
      "end_time": 310409.0,
      "text": "the proof that cultural buildings should not be intimidating."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 310434.0,
      "end_time": 314600.0,
      "text": "They should create a sense of curiosity."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 314879.0,
      "end_time": 317640.0,
      "text": "This is the way to create a cultural place."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 317664.0,
      "end_time": 321522.0,
      "text": "Curiosity is the beginning of a cultural attitude."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 322188.0,
      "end_time": 325722.0,
      "text": "And there&#39;s a piazza there, you can see that piazza."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 326379.0,
      "end_time": 331593.0,
      "text": "And a piazza is the beginning of urban life."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 331617.0,
      "end_time": 334363.0,
      "text": "A piazza is the place where people meet."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 334387.0,
      "end_time": 336396.0,
      "text": "And they mix experience."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 337823.0,
      "end_time": 339455.0,
      "text": "And they mix ages."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 340815.0,
      "end_time": 344965.0,
      "text": "And, you know, in some way,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 344989.0,
      "end_time": 349709.0,
      "text": "you create the essence of the city."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 350470.0,
      "end_time": 356650.0,
      "text": "And since then, we made, in the office, so many other places for people."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 356890.0,
      "end_time": 359840.0,
      "text": "Here, in Rome, is a concert hall."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 360200.0,
      "end_time": 362500.0,
      "text": "Another place for people."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 362290.0,
      "end_time": 366614.0,
      "text": "This building inside is actually designed by the sound, you can see."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 367382.0,
      "end_time": 369148.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s flirting with sound."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 369854.0,
      "end_time": 371830.0,
      "text": "And this is the Kansai Airport,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 372489.0,
      "end_time": 373638.0,
      "text": "in Japan."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 374376.0,
      "end_time": 377215.0,
      "text": "To make a building, sometimes you need to make an island,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 377239.0,
      "end_time": 378835.0,
      "text": "and we made the island."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 379720.0,
      "end_time": 382642.0,
      "text": "The building is more than one mile long."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 383442.0,
      "end_time": 387960.0,
      "text": "It looks like an immense glider, landing on the ground."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 387942.0,
      "end_time": 389926.0,
      "text": "And this is in San Francisco."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 389950.0,
      "end_time": 391616.0,
      "text": "Another place for people."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 391918.0,
      "end_time": 395207.0,
      "text": "This building is the California Academy of Sciences."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 395820.0,
      "end_time": 398585.0,
      "text": "And we planted on that roof --"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 399233.0,
      "end_time": 405560.0,
      "text": "thousands and thousands of plants that use the humidity of the air,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 405584.0,
      "end_time": 408948.0,
      "text": "instead of pumping water from the water table."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 409266.0,
      "end_time": 411466.0,
      "text": "The roof is a living roof, actually."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 411490.0,
      "end_time": 415144.0,
      "text": "And this building was made Platinum LEED."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 415879.0,
      "end_time": 418252.0,
      "text": "The LEED is the system to measure, of course,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 418276.0,
      "end_time": 420689.0,
      "text": "the sustainability of a building."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 421220.0,
      "end_time": 425656.0,
      "text": "So this was also a place for people"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 425680.0,
      "end_time": 428850.0,
      "text": "that will stay a long time."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 428109.0,
      "end_time": 430600.0,
      "text": "And this is actually New York."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 430300.0,
      "end_time": 432409.0,
      "text": "This is the new Whitney,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 432434.0,
      "end_time": 436113.0,
      "text": "in the Meatpacking District in New York."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 437460.0,
      "end_time": 440100.0,
      "text": "Well, another flying vessel."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 441108.0,
      "end_time": 442775.0,
      "text": "Another place for people."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 443807.0,
      "end_time": 446696.0,
      "text": "Here we are in Athens, the Niarchos Foundation."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 446720.0,
      "end_time": 448617.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a library,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 448641.0,
      "end_time": 452331.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s an open house, a concert hall"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 452355.0,
      "end_time": 454246.0,
      "text": "and a big park."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 454270.0,
      "end_time": 459320.0,
      "text": "This building is also a Platinum LEED building."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 460286.0,
      "end_time": 465764.0,
      "text": "This building actually captures the sun&#39;s energy with that roof."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 467140.0,
      "end_time": 472772.0,
      "text": "But, you know, making a building a place for people is good."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 473188.0,
      "end_time": 477340.0,
      "text": "Making libraries, making concert halls,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 477580.0,
      "end_time": 480199.0,
      "text": "making universities, making museums is good,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 480223.0,
      "end_time": 484383.0,
      "text": "because you create a place that&#39;s open, accessible."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 485442.0,
      "end_time": 488484.0,
      "text": "You create a building for a better world, for sure."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 489371.0,
      "end_time": 493842.0,
      "text": "But there is something else"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 493866.0,
      "end_time": 497190.0,
      "text": "that makes architecture amazing, even more."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 497879.0,
      "end_time": 500387.0,
      "text": "And this is the fact that"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 500411.0,
      "end_time": 506235.0,
      "text": "architecture doesn&#39;t just answer to need and necessity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 506259.0,
      "end_time": 512707.0,
      "text": "but also to desires -- yes, desires -- dreams, aspirations."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 513264.0,
      "end_time": 515150.0,
      "text": "This is what architecture does."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 515174.0,
      "end_time": 520708.0,
      "text": "Even the most modest hut on earth"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 520732.0,
      "end_time": 522565.0,
      "text": "is not just a roof."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 522590.00000000006,
      "end_time": 523811.00000000006,
      "text": "It&#39;s more than a roof."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 523835.00000000006,
      "end_time": 525236.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s telling a story;"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 525260.0,
      "end_time": 529766.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s telling a story about the identity of the people living in that hut."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 530427.0,
      "end_time": 531577.0,
      "text": "Individuals."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 532109.0,
      "end_time": 535355.0,
      "text": "Architecture is the art of telling stories."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 536212.0,
      "end_time": 537545.0,
      "text": "Like this one."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 538530.0,
      "end_time": 540918.0,
      "text": "In London: the Shard of Glass."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 540942.0,
      "end_time": 545635.0,
      "text": "Well, this building is the tallest building in Western Europe."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 546130.0,
      "end_time": 551403.0,
      "text": "It goes up more than 300 meters in the air, to breathe fresh air."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 551427.0,
      "end_time": 555172.0,
      "text": "The facets of this building are inclined,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 555196.0,
      "end_time": 559402.0,
      "text": "and they reflect the sky of London, that is never the same."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 559426.0,
      "end_time": 562603.0,
      "text": "After rain, everything becomes bluish."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 563196.0,
      "end_time": 566433.0,
      "text": "In the sunny evening, everything is red."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 567577.0,
      "end_time": 570577.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s something that is difficult to explain."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 571363.0,
      "end_time": 574960.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s what we call the soul of a building."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 575649.0,
      "end_time": 578813.0,
      "text": "On this picture on the left, you have the Menil Collection,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 578837.0,
      "end_time": 580335.0,
      "text": "used a long time ago."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 580359.0,
      "end_time": 581830.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a museum."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 581854.0,
      "end_time": 584497.0,
      "text": "On the right is the Harvard Art Museum."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 584521.0,
      "end_time": 587790.0,
      "text": "Both those two buildings flirt with light."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 588331.0,
      "end_time": 593990.0,
      "text": "Light is probably one of the most essential materials in architecture."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 594789.0,
      "end_time": 596455.0,
      "text": "And this is in Amsterdam."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 597170.0,
      "end_time": 599636.0,
      "text": "This building is flirting with water."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 601162.0,
      "end_time": 604321.0,
      "text": "And this is my office, on the sea."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 605247.0,
      "end_time": 608115.0,
      "text": "Well, this is flirting with work."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 608572.0,
      "end_time": 610993.0,
      "text": "Actually, we enjoy working there."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 611170.0,
      "end_time": 616513.0,
      "text": "And that cable car is the little cable car that goes up to there."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 617633.0,
      "end_time": 620300.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s \"The New York Times\" in New York."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 620840.0,
      "end_time": 624180.0,
      "text": "Well, this is playing with transparency."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 624204.0,
      "end_time": 627804.0,
      "text": "Again, the sense of light, the sense of transparency."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 629363.0,
      "end_time": 632308.0,
      "text": "On the left here, you have the Magic Lantern in Japan,"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 632332.0,
      "end_time": 634355.0,
      "text": "in Ginza, in Tokyo."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 635153.0,
      "end_time": 638870.0,
      "text": "And in the center is a monastery in the forest."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 639419.0,
      "end_time": 643908.0,
      "text": "This monastery is playing with the silence and the forest."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 644855.0,
      "end_time": 647180.0,
      "text": "And a museum, a science museum."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 647831.0,
      "end_time": 649642.0,
      "text": "This is about levitation."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 651339.0,
      "end_time": 654791.0,
      "text": "And this is in the center of Paris,"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 654815.0,
      "end_time": 656910.0,
      "text": "in the belly of the whale."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 656934.0,
      "end_time": 659545.0,
      "text": "This is the PathÃ© Foundation in Paris."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 661178.0,
      "end_time": 664105.0,
      "text": "All those buildings have something in common:"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 664129.0,
      "end_time": 670919.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s that something is searching for desire, for dreams."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 671387.0,
      "end_time": 672536.0,
      "text": "And that&#39;s me."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 672561.0,
      "end_time": 673712.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 673736.0,
      "end_time": 676220.0,
      "text": "Well, it&#39;s me on my sailing boat."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 677855.0,
      "end_time": 679386.0,
      "text": "Flirting with breeze."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 680902.0,
      "end_time": 685857.0,
      "text": "Well, there&#39;s not a very good reason to show you this picture."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 685881.0,
      "end_time": 688814.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 688839.0,
      "end_time": 690783.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m trying, I&#39;m trying."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 690807.0,
      "end_time": 695458.0,
      "text": "You know, one thing is clear: I love sailing, for sure."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 695482.0,
      "end_time": 698549.0,
      "text": "I actually also love designing sailing boats."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 699514.0,
      "end_time": 703971.0,
      "text": "But I love sailing, because sailing is associated with slowness."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 704696.0,
      "end_time": 705974.0,
      "text": "And ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 706887.0,
      "end_time": 708136.0,
      "text": "and silence."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 708934.0,
      "end_time": 710800.0,
      "text": "And the sense of suspension."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 711641.0,
      "end_time": 714410.0,
      "text": "And there is another thing that this picture says."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 714831.0,
      "end_time": 716887.0,
      "text": "It says that I&#39;m Italian."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 716911.0,
      "end_time": 719149.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 719173.0,
      "end_time": 722545.0,
      "text": "Well, there is very little I can do about that."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 722569.0,
      "end_time": 723925.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 724300.0,
      "end_time": 727108.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m Italian, and I love beauty."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 727720.0,
      "end_time": 728870.0,
      "text": "I love beauty."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 729649.0,
      "end_time": 733918.0,
      "text": "Well, let&#39;s go sailing, I want to take you sailing here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 733942.0,
      "end_time": 735237.0,
      "text": "to this place,"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 735792.0,
      "end_time": 738446.0,
      "text": "in the middle of the Pacific Ocean."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 740156.0,
      "end_time": 743695.0,
      "text": "This is the Jean-Marie Tjibaou Center."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 743720.0,
      "end_time": 746545.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s for the Kanaky ethnic group."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 746569.0,
      "end_time": 748924.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s in NoumÃ©a, New Caledonia."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 749899.0,
      "end_time": 751979.0,
      "text": "This place is for art."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 752300.0,
      "end_time": 753425.0,
      "text": "Art and nature."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 754549.0,
      "end_time": 759340.0,
      "text": "And those buildings actually flirt with the wind,"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 759580.0,
      "end_time": 760637.0,
      "text": "with the trade winds."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 761229.0,
      "end_time": 764570.0,
      "text": "They have a sound, they have a voice, those buildings."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 764594.0,
      "end_time": 767538.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m showing this because it&#39;s about beauty."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 767848.0,
      "end_time": 769904.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s about pure beauty."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 770442.0,
      "end_time": 773529.0,
      "text": "And let&#39;s talk about beauty for a moment."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 773887.0,
      "end_time": 777323.0,
      "text": "Beauty is like the bird of paradise:"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 778296.0,
      "end_time": 782600.0,
      "text": "the very moment you try to catch it, it flies away."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 782990.0,
      "end_time": 784699.0,
      "text": "Your arm is too short."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 786236.0,
      "end_time": 790326.0,
      "text": "But beauty is not a frivolous idea."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 791149.0,
      "end_time": 792349.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s the opposite."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 793284.0,
      "end_time": 795919.0,
      "text": "In my native language, that is Italian,"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 795943.0,
      "end_time": 797730.0,
      "text": "\"beautiful\" is \"bello.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 799236.0,
      "end_time": 803569.0,
      "text": "In Spanish, \"beauty\" is \"belleza.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 804809.0,
      "end_time": 808526.0,
      "text": "In Greek, \"beautiful\" is \"kalos.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 810214.0,
      "end_time": 815167.0,
      "text": "When you add \"agathos,\" that means \"beautiful and good.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 815191.0,
      "end_time": 819977.0,
      "text": "In no one of those languages, \"beautiful\" just means \"beautiful.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 820100.0,
      "end_time": 821660.0,
      "text": "It also means \"good.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 823295.0,
      "end_time": 827204.0,
      "text": "Real beauty is when the invisible"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 828220.0,
      "end_time": 831983.0,
      "text": "joins the visible, coming on surface."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 832300.0,
      "end_time": 836996.0,
      "text": "And this doesn&#39;t apply only to art or nature."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 838507.0,
      "end_time": 843881.0,
      "text": "This applies to science, human curiosity, solidarity --"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 843905.0,
      "end_time": 847275.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s the reason why you may say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 847299.0,
      "end_time": 850584.0,
      "text": "\"This is a beautiful person,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 850609.0,
      "end_time": 852405.0,
      "text": "\"That&#39;s a beautiful mind.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 853483.0,
      "end_time": 857689.0,
      "text": "This, this is the beauty that can change people"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 857714.0,
      "end_time": 858912.0,
      "text": "into better people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 858936.0,
      "end_time": 862256.0,
      "text": "by switching a special light in their eyes."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 862672.0,
      "end_time": 865387.0,
      "text": "And making buildings for this beauty"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 865411.0,
      "end_time": 868930.0,
      "text": "makes cities better places to live."
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 868863.0,
      "end_time": 870409.0,
      "text": "And better cities"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 871196.0,
      "end_time": 873102.0,
      "text": "make better citizens."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 874244.0,
      "end_time": 877148.0,
      "text": "Well, this beauty --"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 877172.0,
      "end_time": 879751.0,
      "text": "this universal beauty, I should say --"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 881140.0,
      "end_time": 884480.0,
      "text": "is one of the few things that can change the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 886850.0,
      "end_time": 889727.0,
      "text": "Believe me, this beauty will save the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 890363.0,
      "end_time": 893561.0,
      "text": "One person at a time, but it will do it."
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 895402.0,
      "end_time": 896632.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 896656.0,
      "end_time": 902210.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}